  "detailed_description": "<i>Night Fright is a First Person Psychological Horror Game</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game:</h2>Discover a haunting tale of a father, who driven by madness, tragically killed his daughter. Set in a bleak, atmospheric house, you experience the father's deteriorating mind. As the father goes deeper into his own nightmare, he must confront the devastating consequences of his actions, making for an unsettling experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Explore the house and search for crucial items such as <i>Keys, Lighters, VHS Tapes etc.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/aed44be09a06a62c126d4973b2c71f91.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>As you advance further, you'll encounter unsettling paranormal activities. Investigate them but be careful as you are defenseless against those hiding in the shadows.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Puzzles scattered around must be solved to open routes and progress further.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Death may be inevitable at some point but try to avoid getting caught.",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Night Fright is a First Person Psychological Horror Game</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game:</h2>Discover a haunting tale of a father, who driven by madness, tragically killed his daughter. Set in a bleak, atmospheric house, you experience the father's deteriorating mind. As the father goes deeper into his own nightmare, he must confront the devastating consequences of his actions, making for an unsettling experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/cf2ebfe80c63b81afc778e422cd206dc.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>Explore the house and search for crucial items such as <i>Keys, Lighters, VHS Tapes etc.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/aed44be09a06a62c126d4973b2c71f91.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br>As you advance further, you'll encounter unsettling paranormal activities. Investigate them but be careful as you are defenseless against those hiding in the shadows.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/fca6946709d81e0c83faf7b2d0072921.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Puzzles scattered around must be solved to open routes and progress further.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.poster.avif?t=1738922689\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.webm?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3162740/extras/c2870bda981985036bff97e964af60f0.mp4?t=1738922689\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Death may be inevitable at some point but try to avoid getting caught.",
